ite House was demolished in October, before construction of a new ballroom. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-02/260226-trump-white-house-ballroom-vl-458p-cdb73a.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1333" width="2000"><media:credit>Jon Elswick</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Artist renderings and diagrams of the new White House East Wing and Ballroomoom</media:text><media:description type="plain">An excavator in the rubble after the East Wing of the White House was demolished in October, before construction of a new ballroom. </media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260426-white-house-ballroom-ww-830-572af3.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 17:29:07 GMT</pubDate><title>Republicans propose $1 billion in taxpayer dollars to secure Trump ballroom</title><updateDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 17:36:37 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Daniel Arkin</dc:creator><dc:contributor>Jason Abbruzzese</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Lauren Wilson</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Rebecca Keegan</dc:contributor><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 05 May 2026 20:02:06 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Newly unsealed documents in the legal battle between “It Ends With Us” co-stars Blake Lively and Justin Baldoni pull back the curtain on a monthslong courtroom clash that riveted the entertainment industry</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/unsealed-court-documents-reveal-lively-baldoni-legal-saga-rcna343692</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/unsealed-court-documents-reveal-lively-baldoni-legal-saga-rcna343692</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260505-blake-lively-justin-baldoni-mn-10